    "The scope of the work was to develop LLM-based processes for automated data extraction, software programming to perform the NMA and interpretation of the results from the NMA (highlighted with red in Fig. 1).",
    "Manual assessments of study heterogeneity and suitability of studies for inclusion in an NMA were conducted prior to automation.",
    "Methods Case StudiesThe ability of the LLM to replicate the results of manually conducted NMAs was tested using four case studies.",
    "For each of these case studies, a literature review had been conducted to identify relevant trials, followed by a feasibility analysis to determine which trials were appropriate to include in the NMA, i.e.",
